Mauritius to Increase Container Handling Charges, l’Express Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-12-12T06:05:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-12/mauritius-to-increase-container-handling-charges-l-express-says.html
Mauritius’s Cargo Handling Corp.
plans to increase container charges in October 2012 based on the
country’s inflation rate, l’Express reported, citing Jacques
Faustin, the state-owned port operator’s acting director-
general.  Charges rose 7 percent in October, the Port Louis-based
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in  Port Louis  at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  